Recommended
public static class Recommended.VPCMMLearner
extends SequenceAnnotatorLearner

Uses the voted perceptron algorithm to learn a "conditional Markov model" (CMM). This is analogous to an MEMM learner, and often (surprisingly!) competitive in terms of performance.
